column8: o8udO5vjhFIPublished on Jun 15, 2017Prime Minister Najib Abdul Razak may have given a possible indicator of when the next general election will be held, after announcing the date for the tabling of Budget 2018 in Parliament.According to a Bernama report on Najib's keynote address at the Budget 2018 Consultative Council Meeting in Putrajaya, the fiscal plan is expected to be tabled in Parliament on Oct 27.
